Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.62,0:00:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}快回座位,要上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.10,0:00:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}蛮漂亮的\N在说什么快点要上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.54,0:00:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}快点坐好,教科书拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}不好好认真无法升级喔\N但老师穿这样无法专心上课
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.26,0:00:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你在说什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.70,0:00:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}我很认真酌\N不好好念书无法升大学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.98,0:00:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}那个同学别睡了 快点起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.74,0:00:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}起床啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.14,0:01:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.34,0:01:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}关口同学,快点起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.26,0:01:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}关口同学起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.18,0:01:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.06,0:01:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.50,0:01:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}快点准备
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.86,0:01:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}看什么,快点拿出教科书\N老师屁股好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.26,0:01:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}在说什么?快点拿出翼硎书
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.82,0:01:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}大家把教科书打开\N翻开100页的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.42,0:01:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老师的服装不错喔\N你在说什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:02:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你是大家中成绩最好的你知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.54,0:02:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}安静不要笑,开始上课
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.34,0:02:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老师都穿这样子上课吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.42,0:02:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}很怪吗\N是不是会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.98,0:02:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}我都这样穿啊\N你都穿这样搭电车?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.14,0:02:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}当然啊,别说一些舞苹又\N别再说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.74,0:02:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}翻开100页．乖乖上课
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.06,0:02:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}英国在17世纪之后\N正式进入工业社会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.94,0:02:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}成为世界第一个工业国家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:03:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}不要分心．看这里喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.98,0:03:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}好好记下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.78,0:03:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你在看什么啦?\N是这一页吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.98,0:03:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}好好拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.86,0:03:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}继续喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.26,0:03:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}16世纪三角贸易结束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.22,0:03:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}之后的贸易都集中在…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.02,0:03:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老师我有不懂的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.06,0:03:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.06,0:03:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}关于三角贸易…三角是指那里2
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.82,0:03:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你问这什么问题?\N这里有写啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}这三个地方形成一个三角形\N所以称为三角贸易
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}笔记本上面也有写吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}不要一直乱动啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.74,0:04:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}集中精神上课啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.94,0:04:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}快一点专心上课
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.54,0:04:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你要说什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.22,0:04:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老师能再教我一次吗?\N你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.82,0:04:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老师我想再听一次\N我都讲很多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}怎么可能会有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.78,0:05:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你在说什么?快念书
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.42,0:05:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}我喜欢紫色的\N你在说什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.02,0:05:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老师紫色的内裤不错喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}不要乱看,你还是高中生\N你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你也别一直看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.86,0:05:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你都没在看书啊?\N我在讲这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.74,0:05:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你刚刚有听吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.82,0:05:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}好好听课
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.42,0:05:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}等一下我讲的要记下来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}听说她没有男友\N真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}好想看她自慰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.50,0:06:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}不错喔！丁字裤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.62,0:06:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}她一定没穿胸罩吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.70,0:07:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}荒木同学别聊天\N快点抄笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}大家也快点抄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}完全没在抄啊\N好好抄下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.42,0:07:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}快点抄下来\N把重点抄下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.14,0:07:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}专心上课抄笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.22,0:08:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老师总是穿这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.70,0:08:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}是啊,很─怪吗?\N有点 请转到后面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}那里会奇怪啊?\N是不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.22,0:08:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}有那么怪吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.34,0:08:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}我在百货公司买的\N是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.46,0:08:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}那么奇怪吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.98,0:08:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}透明的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.26,0:08:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}有那么奇怪吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.10,0:08:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}很漂亮啊\N不会奇怪吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.42,0:08:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}不会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}只有老师适合穿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}快点继续喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}从这一页开始喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.46,0:09:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}17世纪的文化是绝对专制\N都是由宫廷世家组成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}当时已经出口许多咖啡茶叶等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.42,0:09:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}当时相当她繁荣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.22,0:09:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}也造成很大的流行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.14,0:10:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}怎么了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}有不会念的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.50,0:10:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}快点继续念
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.22,0:10:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}当时在宫廷的统治下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.18,0:10:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你是怎么了啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.74,0:10:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}维接了一段繁荣的时期
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.78,0:11:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}当时荷兰帝国也很兴盛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}当时的文化受到人民喜爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.18,0:11:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}怎么了?各位
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.06,0:11:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}专心上课喔\N我是有由专心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.30,0:11:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}完全没有专心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}我们会专心的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.54,0:12:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}这样子根本无法进步\N那也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.74,0:12:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你们在说什么啦?\N好好专心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.70,0:12:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}安静一点,看教科
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.78,0:12:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}不要讲些废话了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}大家是怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}各位是怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}专心一点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}大家心都飘走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.10,0:12:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}是怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.74,0:13:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}关回同学怎么站来?\N快点坐下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.54,0:13:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}看老师看到入迷\N你在说什么?快点坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.94,0:13:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}可以吗?\N你的座位也那边吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.94,0:13:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}那边喔,快点坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.26,0:13:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老师无法专心了\N你在说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}看教科书
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.14,0:13:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}都没在抄笔记耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}我会专心的\N真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.26,0:13:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}真的有在看吗?\N有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.86,0:13:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}有在看啊\N快点念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.62,0:14:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}笔记根本是空白的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你为什么要站着呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}那里呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.10,0:14:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}上课怎么可以站着?\N都是老师害的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.02,0:14:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你在说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}都是老师害的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}那是因为你不专心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.26,0:14:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}因为不专心才站起来吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.10,0:14:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}都是老师害的\N你在说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.14,0:14:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}不要怪在老师头上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.54,0:14:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}专已上课
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}都是老师害的\N就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:14:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}不要找借口了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.10,0:15:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}怎么了呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.58,0:15:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}关口同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}这是怎么?你在干嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}关口同学这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.34,0:15:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}这是什么?\N好好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.38,0:15:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}我也想要\N在上课中喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.98,0:15:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}这是怎样啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.82,0:15:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你为什么站着?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}大家干嘛站着啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.78,0:15:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}在上课中喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}因为老师穿这样的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.54,0:16:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}那是因为你不专心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.42,0:16:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你们在干嘛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.86,0:16:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你们真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}在开什么玩笑啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}好兴奋啊\N要专心上课啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你也是,怎么都站着了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.50,0:17:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}快点收起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.70,0:17:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.18,0:17:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}这么大怎么收起来啦?\N快点收起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.38,0:17:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}快点收起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.46,0:17:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你在干嘛?快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.02,0:17:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}不要摩擦我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}都流汁了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.34,0:19:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}丁字裤喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老师脱掉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.78,0:20:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老师的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.34,0:20:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.46,0:20:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}腿抬起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.26,0:20:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.82,0:21:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老师你自己看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.54,0:21:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}好棒喔\N老师也湿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.06,0:21:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}不要乱说话啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.70,0:21:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老师都是你害我这样的你要负责啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.06,0:21:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}只要解决我们的问题我们会认真念书
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.46,0:21:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}真的吗?\N真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.82,0:21:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}真拿你们没办法耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.30,0:21:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}要专心念书喔\N好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.54,0:21:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}要答应我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.58,0:22:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你能答应我好好念书吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.70,0:22:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}变好大喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.78,0:23:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.70,0:24:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}有亲嘴过吗?\N没有
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.30,0:24:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}所以无法专心上课
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.78,0:24:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}嘴巴张开
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.66,0:24:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}好性感
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.14,0:25:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}看清楚喔
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.54,0:25:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.94,0:25:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}好棒乳头硬了\N硬了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.34,0:25:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}我没穿胸罩,乳头硬了\N硬了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.50,0:25:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}记得喔
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.46,0:27:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}乳头硬了吧 继续搓揉
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.38,0:27:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}知道在摸那里吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.50,0:27:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}这硬硬的地方是阴蒂喔
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.42,0:28:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}看了之后要好好念书喔
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.30,0:29:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}仔细看已经湿了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.34,0:29:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}这里
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.90,0:29:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}是插入老二的地方喔
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.54,0:29:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}快点看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.18,0:30:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}超棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.66,0:30:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}好取喔！\N真的耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.58,0:31:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}就是这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.62,0:31:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}不要停
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.22,0:32:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}阴蒂变好大喔\N真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.06,0:32:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}这样无法专心上课吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.58,0:33:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}这里很爽吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.22,0:35:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老师口交到高潮了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.86,0:36:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}想插进老师的小穴吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.38,0:36:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}当然想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.74,0:36:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}那要认真念书喔
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.14,0:36:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}看清楚喔
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.18,0:37:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老二要插进去了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.98,0:37:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}有看到吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.86,0:37:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}好棒,插好深喔
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.02,0:37:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}插好深喔
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.58,0:39:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}这里
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.46,0:39:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}这里喔
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.42,0:40:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}就是那里,插进来
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.18,0:40:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}有看到吗?\N有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.94,0:40:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}插探一点喔
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.18,0:41:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}过来
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.70,0:42:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}好清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.38,0:42:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}插好深喔
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.74,0:43:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}超爽的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.38,0:43:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.10,0:44:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}射好多喔
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.70,0:44:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老师没问题吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.34,0:45:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}好好念书喔
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.66,0:45:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}怎么会这样?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.46,0:45:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}太无聊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.86,0:45:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}快回座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.26,0:45:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老师今天好性感喔
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.54,0:45:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}那开始上课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.14,0:46:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老师在上课之前是不是玩一下\N玩一下?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.86,0:46:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}随时都可以玩吧?\N你成绩最差好好上课
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.86,0:46:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}稍微玩一下之后再念书\N效果会比较好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.30,0:46:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}那今天的进度是十页\N上完之后再来玩
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.18,0:46:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老师不要再补习了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.14,0:46:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}不是说你成绩最差了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.50,0:46:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}教科书要打开喔
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.30,0:46:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}这一题谁会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.86,0:47:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}要认真念书喔
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.94,0:47:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}有问题吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.22,0:47:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}那继续上课喔
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.50,0:47:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}再说一次
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.50,0:47:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}运动
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.34,0:47:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}发音有点怪喔
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.74,0:47:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你有教科书吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.30,0:47:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}我有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.42,0:47:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}有想上课吗?\N有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.30,0:47:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.86,0:48:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}打开第八页喔
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.58,0:48:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你在看哪里呢?请打开
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.66,0:48:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你没打开啊?打开
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.46,0:48:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}第八页喔
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.82,0:48:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你在看什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.82,0:48:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}感觉你很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.06,0:48:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老师的衣服那里买的?\N我平常都这样穿
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.02,0:48:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}都去那里买的呢?\N跟你们没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.82,0:48:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}快点专心上课\N我们无法专心
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.34,0:48:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}穿这样是我的兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.86,0:48:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}好可爱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.38,0:49:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}这根上课无关吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.58,0:49:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}告诉我们的话我们会认真上课
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.74,0:49:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你们别一直看这里\N看教科书
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.30,0:49:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你们都是不及格喔\N知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.50,0:49:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}不要看我了看书\N快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.42,0:49:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你们快一点看教科书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.98,0:49:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}完全没有进展
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.78,0:49:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}先把笔记抄下来
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.10,0:50:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}有抄下来了吧?\N有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.70,0:50:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}要理解才行
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.46,0:50:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}谁知道这句的意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.22,0:50:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老师,你喜欢什么颜色呢\N好想知道喔
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.90,0:50:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}我喜欢红色的但不重要专心上课
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.58,0:50:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你懂吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.66,0:50:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老师我坐不住了\N快点坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.74,0:51:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}快点乖乖听话
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.22,0:51:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}我没有分手
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.38,0:51:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}怎么了?关口同学\N老师你礼拜六在干嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.90,0:51:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}就是在帮你们补习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.70,0:51:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}是想去厕所吗\N没有
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.50,0:51:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}关口同学别再站着了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.38,0:51:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}我最近忙的你们的考试\N你快点回座位
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.38,0:51:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}就是这样大家才不及格喔
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.70,0:51:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}都没有抄笔记啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.10,0:52:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}快点坐下来
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.58,0:52:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}要上课了,不专心的话\N无法升上二年级喔
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.46,0:52:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}无法升级喔\N请专心上课
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.26,0:52:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}抄在笔记上面喔
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.26,0:52:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}要去理解喔
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.66,0:52:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}谁懂这句─意思呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.66,0:52:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}那我来。说好了\N老师再念一次
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.62,0:52:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}那里呢?全部吗?\N全部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.98,0:53:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}知道这什么意思吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.58,0:53:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}好快啊．再一次\N很快吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.58,0:53:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}慢一点\N那我念慢一点
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.74,0:53:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}一定要听清楚喔
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.46,0:53:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}再念一次吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.02,0:53:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}应该懂了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.70,0:54:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}我再念一次喔
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.26,0:54:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}懂吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.46,0:54:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老师我们就是这样才不及格
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.98,0:54:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老师不太懂可以一一教我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.50,0:55:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}CLUB吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.74,0:55:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}那里有写呢\N请你坐好
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.58,0:55:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}快回座位不然会不及格
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.98,0:55:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}这是…\N什么意思呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.38,0:55:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}意思是活动
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.94,0:55:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}坐下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.14,0:55:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}各位别站起来\N我会再说一次的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.34,0:55:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}懂吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.98,0:55:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}这是活动的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.46,0:56:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你们要看清楚喔
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.26,0:56:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}教科书是这里喔
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.74,0:56:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你快一点坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.18,0:57:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}那开始上课了喔\N我再念一次
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.94,0:57:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}我刚说明过了,懂吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.18,0:57:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你也干嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.54,0:57:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}那你说明一次给我听\N有在听课吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.30,0:57:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}有记起来吗?\N你们都不及格吧?好好念
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.82,0:58:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}我过去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.54,0:58:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你们成续都很差
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.38,0:58:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}写下来,笔记根本没开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.90,0:58:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你快点坐下来\N我受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.58,0:58:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}不用忍耐没关系\N你自己站起来的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.02,0:58:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}快点回座位上专心上课\N我们有专心上课
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.10,0:58:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}为什么上课要站起来呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.98,0:59:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老师上课感觉还不错\N那就坐下来
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.18,0:59:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}有学生上课站着的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.06,0:59:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}别站着
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.94,0:59:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}都是老师害的啊\N关我什么事啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.58,0:59:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}就是老师害大家站着\N别说了,快点坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.06,0:59:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}还在上课中别站着
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.70,0:59:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}坐下,别站着
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.10,0:59:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}听好,坐下
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.10,1:00:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}我们都不及格
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.86,1:00:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}大家冷静好好上课吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.86,1:00:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}快坐下
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.66,1:00:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}专心念书
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.06,1:00:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}都是老师害我们的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.22,1:00:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}不要怪在我头上
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.98,1:00:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你也一样
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.70,1:00:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你也硬了吗?\N那都是老师害的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.70,1:00:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}就是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.82,1:00:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}我怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.02,1:00:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老师喜欢红色的吧?\N对啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.26,1:01:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}我们看到老师的内裤\N你们偷看了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.98,1:01:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}那是老师自己打让我们看\N我才不会
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.42,1:01:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老师穿这样都看光了\N你们一直在看啊?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.58,1:01:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}不想看也不行啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.14,1:01:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}都是老师穿红内裤害的\N我们J青春期一下子就硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.34,1:01:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老师要负卖啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.46,1:01:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}怎么会露出来呢\N你有穿内裤吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.18,1:01:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}我有穿啊,受不了了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.38,1:02:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}快点收起来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.78,1:02:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}没有老师穿那么短的内裤啦
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.06,1:02:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}那是老师的兴趣\N都是者师的兴趣害我们的
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.34,1:02:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}快一点收好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.50,1:02:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}受不了了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.30,1:02:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}快一点收起来
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.18,1:02:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}这样怎么念书呢 根本没办法啊\N还是可以啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.74,1:02:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}无法专心念书啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.94,1:02:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}让我们爽的话就念书
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.70,1:02:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}这样子根本无法念书\N快点坐下
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.02,1:02:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}快点收好啦
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.58,1:03:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}这样子根本没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.18,1:03:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}拜托啦\N我们在补习喔
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.78,1:03:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}知道啦\N那就快点收起来
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.46,1:03:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}不要靠近过来啦
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.42,1:03:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}快点收起来啦
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.98,1:04:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}我们会乖乖听话的\N关这根悻子什么事呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.58,1:04:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}快点收起来\N我们会认真念书的
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.10,1:04:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}真的会念书吧?\N会啊
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.22,1:04:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}不能再让我生气要认真念书
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.94,1:04:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}好的
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.06,1:04:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}答应我吗?\N答应你
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.66,1:04:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}不能说出去喔\N好的
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.70,1:05:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}接吻\N好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.86,1:05:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}舌头伸出来
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.22,1:05:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你们在旁边看
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.06,1:05:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}好棒的声音
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.18,1:05:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}真的吗?爽吗?\N老师帮你舔
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.98,1:06:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}如何呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.42,1:06:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}衬衫脱掉喔
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.66,1:06:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}想要舔我胸部吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.70,1:07:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}想知道
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.06,1:07:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}这就是胸部喔
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.30,1:07:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}这是乳头喔
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.10,1:07:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}会出在考题吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.30,1:07:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}舒服的英文怎么说
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.98,1:07:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}乳头很爽\N你们让我说看看
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.70,1:07:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老师受不了了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.74,1:08:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}乳头很2爽的话\N我都会说感觉很棒
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.86,1:08:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}想舔吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.90,1:08:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}想舔吧
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.06,1:08:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}兴奋了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.02,1:09:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}红红的
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.98,1:09:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}想要看看
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.74,1:10:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}知道英文怎么说吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.70,1:10:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}穴吗?\N那是日文啦
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.82,1:10:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}内裤好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.42,1:10:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}好棒喔\N这里好像一条线喔
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.46,1:10:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}好想看喔\N想看我的内裤还是穴呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.38,1:10:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}都想看啊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.86,1:11:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}要记得认真念书喔
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.02,1:11:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}这个结束之后就来上课\N老师看清楚一点
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.22,1:11:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你想要看吧\N对啊
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.86,1:11:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}好老实的小孩喔
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.70,1:12:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}可以了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.38,1:12:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}是这样喔
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.78,1:13:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}好清楚喔
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.30,1:13:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}很清楚吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.38,1:13:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}超帅的耶
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.78,1:14:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}好棒的味道喔\N可以近一点看喔
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.22,1:14:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}谁要用这个指一下呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.02,1:14:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}那里好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.70,1:14:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}除了碰之外想更一步吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.54,1:15:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}闻味道吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.42,1:15:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}什么味道呢?\N不大有味道耶
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.58,1:15:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老师要摸一下吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.62,1:15:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}或者用舔的\N你要帮我舔吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.66,1:17:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.18,1:17:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老师来帮你
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.34,1:18:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你很想要吧\N好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.74,1:18:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老师还自慰…好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.82,1:18:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}那里爽呢了\N深一点的地方
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.54,1:18:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.46,1:19:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}我再含深一点喔
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.34,1:21:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老师我快要不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.10,1:21:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}受不了了,你想怎样?\N我想插老师
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.66,1:21:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}用英文说看看
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.06,1:21:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}我想要插你
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.26,1:21:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}看你那么努力好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.26,1:22:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}想插入吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.74,1:22:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}顶深一点喔
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.62,1:23:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老师快要高潮了\N怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.86,1:23:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}各位有看到插入的地方吧?\N再靠近一点看
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.66,1:24:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}直接插进去
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.54,1:24:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}要看老师高潮的样子喔\N快点打手枪
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.94,1:26:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}要认真念书喔
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.10,1:26:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.10,1:26:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}好可爱喔
Dialogue: 0,2:52:10.83,2:52:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}那是真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:52:19.31,2:52:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}各位回座位\N关口同学
Dialogue: 0,2:52:28.27,2:52:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你们成绩都不及格\N很难上大学喔
Dialogue: 0,2:52:38.51,2:52:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:52:42.83,2:52:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你是成续最差的
Dialogue: 0,2:52:49.71,2:52:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}知道吗?你比谁都差\N你最该认真念书
Dialogue: 0,2:52:56.43,2:52:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,2:52:58.67,2:53:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}什么没关系
Dialogue: 0,2:53:02.67,2:53:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:53:10.51,2:53:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}很怪吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:53:39.15,2:53:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}把教科书打开
Dialogue: 0,2:53:44.75,2:53:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}从那里开始呢?
Dialogue: 0,2:53:55.95,2:54:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}那些来念一下好了
Dialogue: 0,2:54:02.83,2:54:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}就请你先念吧
Dialogue: 0,2:54:11.31,2:54:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}第一,这方法让人无法安心
Dialogue: 0,2:54:33.39,2:54:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}不会念耶\N这汉字不会念吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:55:02.03,2:55:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你这样无法上大学哦
Dialogue: 0,2:55:11.95,2:55:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你在看什么啊?\N专心念书
Dialogue: 0,2:55:18.35,2:55:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}看着教科书
Dialogue: 0,2:55:21.55,2:55:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}这样无发念大学\N好好念书喔
Dialogue: 0,2:55:26.03,2:55:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}大家都一样\N要好好念书才行
Dialogue: 0,2:55:31.47,2:55:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}转到前面去\N先预习一下
Dialogue: 0,2:55:38.99,2:55:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你继续念吧
Dialogue: 0,2:55:46.83,2:55:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}为什么是我啊?\N因为你成绩最差啊
Dialogue: 0,2:55:52.59,2:55:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老师会提出问题\N快点念
Dialogue: 0,2:55:58.83,2:56:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}大家转到前面来
Dialogue: 0,2:56:58.35,2:57:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你来回答这三个问题
Dialogue: 0,2:57:08.43,2:57:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}会回答吧?
Dialogue: 0,2:57:12.91,2:57:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}没问题吧?
Dialogue: 0,2:57:22.19,2:57:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}念错了吧\N我不会啊
Dialogue: 0,2:57:25.39,2:57:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}不是跟老师一起学过吧?
Dialogue: 0,2:57:30.99,2:57:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}好难喔
Dialogue: 0,2:57:34.35,2:57:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}那小野同学念看看
Dialogue: 0,2:57:42.51,2:57:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}不懂
Dialogue: 0,2:57:48.59,2:57:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}为什么不懂呢?
Dialogue: 0,2:57:54.83,2:57:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}这样无法升级喔
Dialogue: 0,2:58:01.71,2:58:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}知道吗?有在听吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:58:08.11,2:58:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}想上大学吧??\N那必须要会念啊
Dialogue: 0,2:58:15.79,2:58:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}难怪你都拿不及格\N有在听吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:58:20.43,2:58:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}关口同学有在听吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:58:59.95,2:59:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}写下来
Dialogue: 0,2:59:03.47,2:59:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}我等一下会写的
Dialogue: 0,2:59:06.99,2:59:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}为什么是等一下呢?
Dialogue: 0,2:59:09.23,2:59:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}快一点 我现在有点忙耶
Dialogue: 0,2:59:12.91,2:59:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}忙吗?你在遮什么?\N现在还在上课喔
Dialogue: 0,2:59:22.35,2:59:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}不懂汉字吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:59:26.51,2:59:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你现在就写下来
Dialogue: 0,2:59:31.95,2:59:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}等一下写好了\N现在在念书喔
Dialogue: 0,2:59:39.63,2:59:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你从刚才遮什么啦
Dialogue: 0,2:59:48.11,2:59:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}这是什么?还在上课中这样
Dialogue: 0,2:59:53.87,2:59:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}这是怎样?知道还在上课中吧?
Dialogue: 0,3:00:02.51,3:00:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}都是老师不好啊\N老师那里不好呢?
Dialogue: 0,3:00:07.31,3:00:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}别再这样做了\N我无法专心
Dialogue: 0,3:00:14.19,3:00:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}敏感什么啦?在上课中耶
Dialogue: 0,3:00:18.19,3:00:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}就是这样子,才会拿低分
Dialogue: 0,3:00:24.43,3:00:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}有在听吗?
Dialogue: 0,3:00:28.43,3:00:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}快点站起来吧
Dialogue: 0,3:00:48.11,3:00:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}大家不这么认为吗?
Dialogue: 0,3:00:54.83,3:00:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}硬成这样喔
Dialogue: 0,3:00:58.51,3:01:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}大家不认为很奇怪吗\N现在是上课中喔
Dialogue: 0,3:01:07.31,3:01:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}为什么会这样呢?
Dialogue: 0,3:01:15.79,3:01:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}大家是怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,3:01:20.27,3:01:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}大家都一样吗?\N为什么?现在还在上课喔
Dialogue: 0,3:01:27.47,3:01:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}懂吗?
Dialogue: 0,3:01:31.31,3:01:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}大家真爱开玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,3:01:52.91,3:01:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你们在干嘛?快收起来
Dialogue: 0,3:02:26.51,3:02:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}这个什么?流出来了
Dialogue: 0,3:02:58.19,3:03:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你们在干嘛啊?
Dialogue: 0,3:03:28.59,3:03:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}你在干嘛啊?
Dialogue: 0,3:03:36.27,3:03:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}只要老师脱的话\N我们一定会考上大学的
Dialogue: 0,3:03:42.03,3:03:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}是认真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,3:04:24.43,3:04:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}答应我喔
Dialogue: 0,3:05:35.79,3:05:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,3:06:00.59,3:06:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老师好棒喔,爽吗?
Dialogue: 0,3:07:43.47,3:07:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老师湿了吗?湿了吗?
Dialogue: 0,3:08:08.43,3:08:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,3:09:04.75,3:09:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}想看老师那边吗?\N想啊
Dialogue: 0,3:09:11.31,3:09:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}要让我们看吗\N让我看
Dialogue: 0,3:10:00.75,3:10:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}好棒的表情,受不了了
Dialogue: 0,3:10:13.71,3:10:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}第一次看耶
Dialogue: 0,3:10:27.31,3:10:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}好想看喔
Dialogue: 0,3:10:29.71,3:10:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老师的那里如何呢?\N我想看
Dialogue: 0,3:10:44.59,3:10:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,3:10:48.43,3:10:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}受不了了
Dialogue: 0,3:12:12.59,3:12:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,3:13:11.15,3:13:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老师让我看看
Dialogue: 0,3:13:15.47,3:13:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}不要看啦\N好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,3:14:09.39,3:14:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}这样被舔又要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,3:14:52.43,3:14:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}变好敏感喔
Dialogue: 0,3:20:59.31,3:21:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}好兴奋喔
Dialogue: 0,3:22:03.95,3:22:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,3:22:23.31,3:22:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}里面好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,3:22:26.99,3:22:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}各位看清楚喔
Dialogue: 0,3:22:44.91,3:22:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,3:23:27.47,3:23:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}插大力一点
Dialogue: 0,3:23:33.07,3:23:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,3:24:15.63,3:24:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}要答应我都考90分以上喔\N好的
Dialogue: 0,3:24:25.55,3:24:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}老师我也想
Dialogue: 0,3:24:38.67,3:24:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}太棒了
Dialogue: 0,3:24:40.75,3:24:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs22\b1}下一个换我好了\N真的吗?

